# Python backend

## Modules

| Module | Role |
|--------|------|
| `poller.py` | 30s loop; compose cmd auto-detect; snapshot diff restart counts; prune >7d |
| `agent.py` | One-shot Claude; `asyncio.Lock` per server_id; max 1 pending action/server |
| `executor.py` | `protected_services` check; health check; fail → new incident, no auto-rollback |
| `db/store.py` | All SQL |
| `tools/*.py` | MCP implementations |

## SSH

- User `root`, key `~/.ssh/id_ed25519` (from yaml).
- Unreachable server → status `unknown`, log, continue other servers.
- journalctl: no sudo → sudo → empty + warning.

## MCP phases

- Phase 1: read-only infra tools only.
- Phase 3+: execution tools; `rollback_deployment` Phase 4 only.
- `repo` arg = `repos.yaml` id → resolve owner/name in `cicd.py`.

## Rollback (Phase 4)

Previous image from last **healthy** snapshot in SQLite; `sed` compose file on VPS.

## Tests

Mock SSH/GitHub; no real network in CI.
